<li id="cite_note-1"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFSmith" class="citation book cs1">Smith, Joseph. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://byustudies.byu.edu/content/volume-4-chapter-27">"Volume 4, Chapter 27"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/History_of_the_Church_(Joseph_Smith)" class="mw-redirect" title="History of the Church (Joseph Smith)">History of the Church</a></i>. p.&#160;461<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">6 April</span> 2018</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Volume+4%2C+Chapter+27&amp;rft.btitle=History+of+the+Church&amp;rft.pages=461&amp;rft.aulast=Smith&amp;rft.aufirst=Joseph&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbyustudies.byu.edu%2Fcontent%2Fvolume-4-chapter-27&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABibliography+of+the+Latter+Day+Saint+movement" class="Z3988"></span></span>
